Package: fplyr
Type: Package
Title: Read files by chunks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Federico", "Marotta", email = "federico.marotta@edu.unito.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: fplyr is a package to read and process a delimited file chunk by
    chunk. A chunk consists of all the rows that have the same value in the
    first field.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
